  "text": "In the open-field test, the animals were placed in the center of a white plastic cage (40 x 33 x 17 cm) containing 16 rectangles (9.5 x 8.5 cm). The number of the covered rectangles for each animal was counted for 5 minutes [CITATION_1] . For analysis, a Sony video-camera and monitor (Sony, United Kingdom) were used. These results were expressed number of rectangles per minute.",
